---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Docs — xisland"
  description="How to install xisland, connect your AI agents, reinstall hooks, and label sessions."
>
  <Nav />
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1>Docs</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Get xisland running in a few minutes.</p>
      </header>

      <div class="toc">
        <a href="#installation">Installation</a>
        <span class="sep">/</span>
        <a href="#reinstall-hooks">Reinstall hooks</a>
        <span class="sep">/</span>
        <a href="#label-session">Label a session</a>
      </div>

      <section id="installation">
        <h2><span class="num">01</span> Installation</h2>

        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <div class="step-title">Download &amp; install</div>
            <p>Download xisland from the <a href="/download" class="link">download page</a>, open the DMG, and drag <strong>xIsland</strong> to your Applications folder.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="step-title">Launch the app</div>
            <p>Open xIsland from Applications. It will appear in your menu bar. The first launch may ask you to allow accessibility permissions — grant them so the app can detect terminal windows.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="step-title">Connect your agents</div>
            <p>Open <strong>Settings → Setup</strong> and enable hooks for each agent you use.</p>

            <table>
              <thead>
                <tr><th>Agent</th><th>What gets installed</th></tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td>Claude Code</td><td>Hook entries in <code>~/.claude/settings.json</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Codex</td><td>Hook entries in <code>~/.codex/hooks.json</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>OpenCode</td><td>Plugin registered with OpenCode</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Gemini CLI</td><td>Hook entries in <code>~/.gemini/settings.json</code></td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <p class="note">Hooks are fail-open — if xIsland is not running, your agents continue normally without any interruption.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="step-title">Install the CLI tool (optional, recommended)</div>
            <p>Still in <strong>Settings → Setup</strong>, find the <strong>Command line</strong> section and click <strong>Install</strong>. This adds <code>xisland</code> to <code>/usr/local/bin</code> so you can control the app from inside any agent session. Requires your admin password once.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section id="reinstall-hooks">
        <h2><span class="num">02</span> Reinstall hooks</h2>

        <p>If an agent update overwrites your hook config, or xIsland shows a warning that hooks are inactive:</p>

        <ol class="steps">
          <li>Open <strong>Settings → Setup</strong>.</li>
          <li>Toggle the affected agent <strong>off</strong>, then <strong>on</strong> again.</li>
        </ol>

        <p>xIsland rewrites the hook entries. No restart required.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="label-session">
        <h2><span class="num">03</span> Label a session</h2>

        <p>Labels give a session a memorable name in the xIsland panel, replacing the default folder name.</p>

        <div class="step-title">From inside an agent</div>
        <p>While a Claude Code or Gemini CLI session is running, type:</p>

        <div class="code-block">
          <code>!xisland rename "Auth refactor"</code>
        </div>

        <p>The <code>!</code> prefix runs the command in your shell without interrupting the agent. The label updates in the panel immediately.</p>

        <p class="note">Requires the <code>xisland</code> CLI — see step 4 of Installation above.</p>

        <div class="priority-box">
          <div class="priority-title">Name priority</div>
          <ol class="priority-list">
            <li><span class="badge">1</span> Your <code>xisland rename</code> label — highest priority</li>
            <li><span class="badge">2</span> Agent-native title (e.g. Claude Code <code>/rename</code>)</li>
            <li><span class="badge">3</span> Working directory name</li>
            <li><span class="badge">4</span> Session ID prefix — fallback</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  main {
    padding: 120px 0 100px;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-3);
  }

  .toc {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-3);
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .toc a {
    color: var(--text-2);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .toc a:hover { color: var(--green); }

  .sep { color: var(--border-2); }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .num {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--green);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  p {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .steps {
    list-style: none;
    counter-reset: steps;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .steps > li {
    counter-increment: steps;
    padding-left: 28px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .steps > li::before {
    content: counter(steps);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 1px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--green);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  table {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 16px 0;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  th {
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--text-3);
    font-weight: 400;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  td {
    color: var(--text-2);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  td:first-child { color: var(--text); }

  code {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--green);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .note {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-3);
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .code-block {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin: 16px 0;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .code-block code {
    background: none;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .priority-box {
    margin-top: 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    max-width: 480px;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
  }

  .priority-title {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-3);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .priority-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .priority-list li {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--bg);
    background: var(--green);
    border-radius: 3px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .link {
    color: var(--green);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(61, 220, 132, 0.4);
  }

  .link:hover {
    text-decoration-color: var(--green);
  }

  strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    main { padding: 100px 0 80px; }
    h1 { font-size: 20px; }
  }
</style>
